141113_PINKERTON_0340_BC4JCDACXX - second run. Lane 5 is still control and still fails, so RTA fails calculation again. Rehyb restart, setting lane 3 as control.

Run works reasonably well, given that lane 3 is set as control and most lanes are overclustered. Cumulative Q30 for all lanes except 5 is in acceptable range.  FWHM fails to calc a few tiles cycle 75, 133 (lane 1), 102 (2), 111 (4-8).

Marked as done 12/1/14 - CE
